{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, this rating method has proven useful during development in tracking multiple hyperparameter settings, even with a handful of evaluators.",
    "Multiple SpeakersFastPitch is easy to extend to multiple speakers.",
    "We have trained a model on the LJSpeech-1.1 dataset with additional internal training data coming from two female speakers: speaker 1 (8330 samples with the total of 13.6 h), and speaker 2 (18995 samples with the total of 17.3 h).",
    "We condition the model on the speaker by adding a global speaker embedding to the input tokens x.",
    "To compare, we have chosen multi-speaker Tacotron 2 and Flowtron [27]."
  ]
}